  "instructions": [
    "Combine vegetable stock, tomato juice, gochujang, soy sauce, rice vinegar, and sugar in a large bowl.",
    "Add naengmyeon to the bowl and toss to coat the noodles with the sauce.",
    "Refrigerate for at least 2 hours to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Just before serving, drizzle lacquer glaze over the noodles if using.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds and chopped green onion over the noodles.",
    "Slice cucumber into thin rounds and serve alongside the noodles."
